Class ChainedResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.esoco.ewt.app.ChainedResource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Resource

    public class ChainedResource
extends java.lang.Object
implements Resource
    A resource implementation that chains two resources. If the lookup in the primary resource fails a lookup in the secondary resource will be performed.
